==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: sīmăzhāo zhī xīn
===Etymology===
*From: '''司馬昭之心''', [[路人]][[皆]][[知]]
Literally: (Even the people in the street know) the heart of [[Wikipedia:Sima Zhao|Sima Zhao]]

===Idiom===
'''[[司馬昭]][[之]][[心]]'''
# evil ambitions that are transparent to everyone.
===Alternate forms===
[[司马昭之心]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

